OL,3,CRestaurant closes following 'dozens of
OL,4,Cracist attacks' and 'physical assault'
OL,6,FBosses of a restaurant in Exeter says
OL,7,Fthey have been forced to close its
OL,8,Fdoors after an alleged physical
OL,9,Fassault left someone "seriously
OL,10,Finjured".
OL,12,FTapas bar La Lola, in Fore Street, has
OL,13,Ftemporarily shut. A sign in the window
OL,14,Fsays staff have been the victim of
OL,15,F"dozens of racist attacks and death
OL,16,Fthreats".
OL,18,FThe sign, which ITV News understands
OL,19,Fwas placed there about a month ago,
OL,20,Fstates: "Last Friday, we suffered a
OL,21,Fphysical assault with serious injuries.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
