OL,3,CRestaurant closes following 'dozens of
OL,4,Cracist attacks' and 'physical assault'
OL,6,F"Over the past year we have filed
OL,7,Fdozens of complaints of racist attacks
OL,8,Fand death threats to both the police,
OL,9,Four landlord and Exeter City Council
OL,10,Fand none of them have done anything to
OL,11,Fstop this violence."
OL,13,FA local city police inspector told ITV
OL,14,FNews the sign "does not reflect the
OL,15,Fcurrent situation" and said Devon and
OL,16,FCornwall Police are working to tackle
OL,17,Fanti-social behaviour.
OL,19,FExeter City Council says it is working
OL,20,Fclosely with police and is in regular
OL,21,Fcontact with the tapas bar's owner.
