OL,6,FThe restaurant says one person was
OL,7,F"seriously injured" as a result of the
OL,8,Falleged assault and confirmed the
OL,9,Frestaurant will "remain closed until
OL,10,FDevon and Cornwall Police or the
OL,11,FExeter City Council can ensure the
OL,12,Fsafety of our customers and out staff".
OL,14,F"Sorry for the inconvenience," it adds.
OL,16,FIn response, Devon and Cornwall Police
OL,17,FInspector Nathan Johnson said: "I am
OL,18,Fin no doubt that the owner of La Lola
OL,19,Fhas suffered from anti-social
OL,20,Fbehaviour."
