OL,6,FBut he said in some instances there
OL,7,Fhas been a "lack of evidence" from
OL,8,FCCTV or engagement from the victim to
OL,9,Fprogress investigations.
OL,11,FHe added: "The challenge I often find
OL,12,Fis that of expectation of the criminal
OL,13,Fjustice system and what is possible
OL,14,Fwithin a legal framework with
OL,15,Favailable evidence and what a victim
OL,16,Fof crime would seek as a suitable
OL,17,Foutcome."
