OL,6,FInspector Johnson said there have been
OL,7,F25 interactions between Devon and
OL,8,FCornwall Police and the owner of La
OL,9,FLola.
OL,11,FHe added that the force takes anti-
OL,12,Fsocial behaviour in Exeter "very
OL,13,Fseriously" and is working with local
OL,14,Fnetworks and organisations to tackle
OL,15,Fthe cause, including addiction and
OL,16,Flong referral times for rehab centres.
OL,18,FIt is also developing a anti-social
OL,19,Fbehaviour action plan for South Street
OL,20,Fand Fore Street, along with the city's
OL,21,FBusiness Improvement District InExeter.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
