OL,6,FSince May this year, the force has
OL,7,Falso increased foot patrols in Exeter
OL,8,FCity Centre to tackle anti-social
OL,9,Fbehaviour and enforce public space
OL,10,Fprotection orders and no alcohol zones.
OL,12,FAn Exeter City Council spokesman said:
OL,13,F"We are sorry to hear of Mr Montes'
OL,14,Fexperiences. We continue to work
OL,15,Fclosely with the police to address
OL,16,Fissues around anti-social behaviour in
OL,17,FExeter.
